node.text:
@hazutohk In HAZUTO's newest Slice N' Serve Set, contemporary forms combine into a visually coherent package.⁣⁣
•⁣⁣
Colourful rims paired with Congo Sapele Wood boards sit on top a Concrete stand that's inspired by river pebbles.⁣⁣
•⁣⁣
It's an imaginative board set that's both a décor piece and a restaurant-level presentation kit.⁣⁣
•⁣⁣
Now 40% off on Kickstarter: ✅ Link in Bio! or in HAZUTO's bio @hazutohk ⁣⁣
•⁣⁣
•⁣⁣
•#Design_Only #architecture #decor #furniture #interior #product #design #art #slice #serve #set #wood #wooden #board #concrete #stand
